  <TITLE>Add support for SimpleConsumer-like access</TITLE>
  <DESCRIPTION>Sometimes apps might not want to be part of a consumer group, or might have trivial consumption patterns such as consuming from a single partition. We can probably expose this pretty cleanly with URLs like GET /topics/foo/partitions/0/messages?offset=100[&amp;count=100], although specifying per-partition offsets at the topic level may get messy.</DESCRIPTION>
